Installation Instructions
=========================

The latest libnxtbt sources can be obtained at <https://github.com/danielmeek32/libnxtbt> and the latest source release at <https://github.com/danielmeek32/libnxtbt/releases/latest>.

Prerequisities
--------------

libnxtbt has no dependencies.

Compiling libnxtbt
------------------

From the directory where the libnxtbt sources are extracted, run:

    $ ./autogen.sh
    $ ./configure
    $ make

libnxtbt uses the GNU Autotools build system, and the configure script supports a wide range of options to customise the way that libnxtbt is built. Please consult the documentation on Autotools for further information.

Installing libnxtbt
-------------------

After compiling nxtcli, run:

    # make install

You will usually need to be root to install libnxtbt, unless you have configured libnxtbt not to install system-wide.

After installation, you may need to update your system's dynamic linker in order to use libnxtbt, especially if you have installed libnxtbt in a non-standard location. Please consult your system's documentation for further information.
